  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you access to this founding mystery, you learn the ability to make air dance around you as you choose. As a bonus action you can activate the air dance, which remains active for a minute, during which your AC increases by your Intelligence modifier and moving away from a creature do not provoke attacks of opportunity.</span> </p>",
